headline: Dover Sees Revenue and Earnings Growth in Q3 2024
summary: Dover ( (DOV) ) has provided an update. Dover Corporation reported a 1% increase in revenue for Q3 2024, reaching $2 billion, with GAAP earnings from continuing operations up 19% to $313 million. The company’s growth was driven by strong performance in clean energy and biopharma, despite challenges in other sectors.
